---
// Banner CTA final
---

<section class="cta-final">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hay una generación<br><span class="marker">esperando ser alcanzada.</span></h2>
    <p>
      Cada día sin vos, hay un joven en un colegio de Costa Rica buscando esperanza.
      Sumate y seamos luz juntos.
    </p>
    <div class="ctas">
      <a href="#sumate" class="btn btn-yellow">Sumate a la misión <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-ghost-light">Conversemos <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-final {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--on-dark);
    padding: 100px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-final::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(252,211,77,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-final h2 { color: var(--on-dark); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .cta-final h2 :global(.marker) {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cta-final p {
    color: var(--on-dark-soft);
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
  }
  .ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cta-final { padding: 80px 0; }
  }
</style>
